{{!
    @template core/form-user-selector-suggestion

    Moodle template for rendering a user suggestion within an autocomplete field.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * id User ID field
    * email User email field
    * idnumber User idnumber field
    * phone1 User phone1 field
    * phone2 User phone2 field
    * department User department field
    * institution User institution field
    * fullname User fullname
    * identity Concatenated list of identity fields
    * profileurl URL to user profile
    * profileimageurl URL to a profile image
    * profileimageurlsmall URL to a small profile image

    Example context (json):
    { "fullname": "Charlie Carrot",
      "identity": "Sales, United Kingdom",
      "profileimageurlsmall": "http://example.com/image.jpg"
    }
}}
<span>
    <img height="12" src="{{profileimageurlsmall}}" alt="" role="presentation">
    <span>{{fullname}}</span>
    {{#identity}}
    <span><small>{{identity}}</small></span>
    {{/identity}}
</span>